-2.png",srcImageSm:"/images/about/about-heroslider-2-sm.png"},{title:"Empowering Potential, Driving Innovation.",desc:"At TVSE, we design solutions that help businesses and individuals achieve their true potential, delivering innovation at the critical mile.",srcImage:"/images/about/about-heroslider-3.png",srcImageSm:"/images/about/about-heroslider-3-sm.png"},{title:"Empowering Potential, Driving Innovation.",desc:"At TVSE, we design solutions that help businesses and individuals achieve their true potential, delivering innovation at the critical mile.",srcImage:"/images/about/about-heroslider-4.png",srcImageSm:"/images/about/about-heroslider-4-sm.png"},{title:"Empowering Potential, Driving Innovation.",desc:"At TVSE, we design solutions that help businesses and individuals achieve their true potential, delivering innovation at the critical mile.",srcImage:"/images/about/about-heroslider-1.png",srcImageSm:"/images/about/about-heroslider-1-sm.png"}]},l5=[{tag:"Mission",heading:"To design innovative products and services that bring ideas and business processes to life at the critical mile.",srcImg:"/images/about/mission-img.png"},{tag:"Vision",heading:"To empower businesses and individuals to achieve their full potential through transformative and homegrown solutions.",srcImg:"/images/about/vision-img.png"}],Gb={tag:"What we value",valueList:[{title:"Persevering for Customer Delight",desc:"Continuously strive to exceed customer expectations with dedication and passion.",iconSrc:"/images/about/persevering-icon.svg"},{title:"Promoting Initiative",desc:"Encourage positivity and proactive steps to drive team and individual success.",iconSrc:"/images/about/initiative-icon.svg"},{title:"Delivering with Integrity",desc:"Commit to inclusivity, honesty, and trust in everything we do.",iconSrc:"/images/about/leadership-icon.svg"},{title:"Fostering Leadership",desc:"Empower employees by nurturing leadership at all levels.",iconSrc:"/images/about/fostering-leadership-icon.svg"},{title:"Excellence & Operational Efficiency",desc:"Set high standards, deliver the best in every role, and drive real value through operational excellence.",iconSrc:"/images/about/excellence-icon.svg"},{title:"Commitment to CSR & Sustainability",desc:"Uplift communities through CSR initiatives and embrace sustainable practices for lasting impact.",iconSrc:"/images/about/commitment-icon.svg"}]},sp=[{year:"1986-1990",image:"/images/about/1986-1990.png",data:["Foundation of TVS Electronics","Inaugurated Tumakuru factory","Launched first offline UPS – Aegis & Elgar","Manufactured computer peripherals – MSP Printer and 84-key keyboard launched"]},{year:"1991-1995",image:"/images/about/1991-1995.png",data:[" CMS of UPS systems for IMV","Supplies for Victron Energy","Launched TVS mechanical keyboard, designed and manufactured in-house"]},{year:"1996-2000",image:"/images/about/1996-2000.png",data:["Won MAIT Awards for Business Excellence & Exports","Inaugurated Chennai factory","Launched India’s first language printer and rolled out the first print head","Contract manufacturing of rectifiers for Tyco","PC Quest User Choice Award for DMP"]},{year:"2001-2005",image:"/images/about/2001-2005.png",data:[" Launched India’s first POS – TVS Sprint","PC Quest User Choice Award for DMP","Sold over 1 million keyboards & printers","Ranked in Deloitte Touche Tohmatsu’s Asia Pacific Tech Fast 500 (Top 250)","International expansion with the launch of the International Language Printer","Launched Made in India STB"]},{year:"2006-2010",image:"/images/about/1986-1990.png",data:["Dell service partnership – Pan India support for laptops and PCs","Exclusive service centres for HTC","Supported Banktech, NCR Corporation, and Diebold","Break-fix services for Lenovo"]},{year:"2011-2015",image:"/images/about/2011-2015.png",data:["Repairs & refurbishment of Sony consumer products","Support for Samsung and LG mobile phones","Flagship service centre for Samsung","Support for Xiaomi distribution busines