up, and universal compatibility for everyday connections.",srcImg:"/images/all-products/webcam-thumb.png",targetRoute:"/category/web-camera"}]},yd={tag:"Billing Software",heading:"Billing Software Solutions",desc:"Amplify your business by scaling with seamless retail software solutions tailored to your specific needs, size, and industry and compatible with the TVS-E product ecosystem.",softwareList:[{title:"TVS-E Pay",desc:"TVS-E Pay is our in-house, user-friendly billing app designed to improve billing efficiency, simplify accounting, boost revenue and achieve profitability specifically for small and medium businesses.",srcImg:"/images/all-products/tvse-pay-thumb.png",targetRoute:"/#"},{title:"SnapBizz",desc:"Making virtual supermarkets out of Kiranas, by providing a competitive advantage and increased profitability with Snapbizz- secure cloud-based mobile solution. ",srcImg:"/images/all-products/snapbizz-thumb.png",targetRoute:"/#"},{title:"QueueBuster",desc:"Designed for small, medium, and large retail firms, QueueBuster is our versatile and customisable solution that improves processes, increases revenue and streamlines operations.",srcImg:"/images/all-products/queuebuster-thumb.png",targetRoute:"/#"},{title:"RoyalPOS",desc:"Convert your smartphone into a business point of sale with TVS-E Royal POS. Enjoy centralised inventory control, outlet management and  delivery partners to ensure optimal retail efficiency.",srcImg:"/images/all-products/royalpos-thumb.png",targetRoute:"/#"}]},N1="/images/arrow-primary-bg.svg",E1=({title:e,desc:t,srcImg:i,targetRoute:r})=>n.jsxs("div",{className:"space-y-[26px]",children:[n.jsx(ue,{to:r,children:n.jsx("img",{src:i,alt:"blog-thumb",className:"h-[358px] w-full object-cover mb-6.5"})}),n.jsx("h5",{className:"md:line-clamp-1 font-light",children:e}),n.jsx("span",{className:"block border-t border-[#B5B5B5] w-full"}),n.jsx("p",{className:"max-w-[345px] line-clamp-3 md:max-w-full",children:t}),n.jsxs(ue,{to:r,className:"flex items-