ystems propel your business forward with excellent processing capabilities for tasks at scale."}]},u0=[{title:"Large format Retail",iconSrc:"/images/all-products/largeformat-retail-icon.svg"},{title:"Hospital and Pharmacies",iconSrc:"/images/all-products/hospital-icon.svg"},{title:"Electronics & Consumer Durables",iconSrc:"/images/all-products/electronics-icon.svg"},{title:"Quick Service Restaurants",iconSrc:"/images/all-products/quick-service-icon.svg"},{title:"Neighborhood Kirana Stores",iconSrc:"/images/all-products/neighborhood-icon.svg"},{title:"Supermarkets",iconSrc:"/images/all-products/supermarket-icon.svg"}],GL=[{title:"What is a POS system?",desc:"A POS (Point of Sale) system is a combination of software and hardware designed to facilitate and streamline sales transactions, inventory management, and payment processing at retail stores, restaurants, and other businesses. A touch POS system or a touch screen POS system, offers a user-friendly interface that allows staff to process sales transactions quickly and efficiently by tapping on the screen."},{title:"Why does your business need a POS system?",desc:"Investing in a POS system offers numerous benefits to businesses, including increased efficiency, better inventory management, and improved customer service. Some reasons to consider implementing a touch POS system in your business are: <br/><br/><strong>Faster transaction processing:</strong> Touch screen POS systems enable employees to process transactions quickly, reducing wait times for customers. <br/></br> <strong>Improved accuracy:</strong> Touch POS machine minimize the risk of human error by automating sales transactions and inventory tracking.<br/><br/> <strong>Enhanced reporting and analytics:</strong> POS machine provide valuable insights into sales trends and customer behavior, helping businesses make informed decisions and improve their bottom line. <br/><br/> <strong>Easy integration with other business tools:</strong> Many POS machines can be integrated with accounting software, CRM systems, and other business tools for seamless data management."},{title:"Factors to consider when buying a POS system",desc:"When selecting a POS system for your business, consider the following factors: <br/><br/> <strong>Budget:</strong> Compare POS machine price, touch POS machine price, and android POS billing machine price to find a system that fits within your budget. <br/><br/> <strong>Compatibility:</strong> Ensure the POS system is compatible with your existing hardware and software, such as barcode scanners, receipt printers, and accounting software. <br/><br/> <strong>Ease of use: </strong> Choose a touch screen POS system with an intuitive user interface that’s easy for your staff to learn and use. <br/><br/> <strong>Scalability:</strong> Look for a POS system provider that offers reliable customer support, including installation, training, and ongoing assistance. <br/><br/> <strong>Scalability:</strong>  Select a POS system that can grow with your business, allowing you to add features and functionality as needed.<br/><br/> <strong>Support:</strong> Look for a POS system provider that offers reliable customer support and regular software updates."},{title:"Which are the Best POS systems",desc:"TVS Electronics offers a range of high-quality POS machines, including touch POS systems, to cater to various business needs. Here are some of the best touch POS machines in our collection: <br/><br/> <strong>TP 415c</strong> <br/>The TP 415c is a versatile touch POS system designed for retail and hospitality businesses. With its sleek design, powerful performance, and user-friendly interface, this touch POS machine is an excellent choice for businesses looking for a reliable and efficient POS solution. <br/><br/> <strong>TP 415CA</strong><br/>Featuring an Android operating system, the TP 415CA touch POS system offers a wide range of features and functionality, including integrated payment processing, inventory management, and customer relationship management.<br/><br/> <strong>TP 415c Pro</strong><br/>The TP 415c Pro touch POS system is designed for businesses that require advanced features and functionality. With its powerful performance, customizable interface, and seamless integration with other business tools, this touch POS machine is an excellent choice for growing businesses.<br/><br/><strong>TP i415C K</strong><br/>The TP i415C K touch POS system is a compact and cost-effective solution for small businesses and startups. This touch screen POS system offers essential features and functionality, including sales transaction processing, inventory management, and payment processing."},{title:"Want to know more about TVS Electronics Touch POS systems? ",desc:"Upgrade your business operations with a high-quality touch POS system from TVS Electronics. Browse our range of touch screen POS systems, POS billing machines, and POS touch screens, and find the perfect solution for your business needs. Buy POS machine from TVS Electronics and enjoy reliable performance, competitive pricing, and exceptional customer support. <br/><br/> TVS Electronics is a leading provider of POS solutions, offering a wide range of TVS POS machines designed to enhance efficiency and streamline business operations. Our touch POS systems are equipped with high-quality POS touch screens, ensuring seamless interaction and improved transaction processing speeds. By choosing a TVS POS machine, you can be confident in the reliability and performance of your POS system. <br/><br/> The POS screen is a critical component of any touch screen POS system, as it directly impacts the user experience. At TVS Electronics, we prioritize providing high-quality POS touch screens that offer excellent responsiveness, durability, and visibility. This ensures that your staff can process transactions quickly and accurately, ultimately improving customer satisfaction. <br/><br/>If you’re looking to upgrade your current POS system or invest in a new touch screen POS solution, now is the perfect time to buy POS machine from TVS Electronics. Our extensive range of touch POS systems caters to businesses of all sizes and types, ensuring you’ll find the ideal solution for your unique requirements. When you buy POS machine from TVS Electronics, you can trust that you’re investing in a high-quality product backed by exceptional customer support and after-sales service."}],WL=({featuredImage:e,featuredContent:t})=>n.jsx("div",{className:"max-w-[1020px] grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-[65px_120px] pt-6",children:t&&t.map((i,r)=>n.jsxs("div",{className:"space-y-8",children:[e[r]!=null?n.jsx("img",{src:e[r],alt:"icon",className:"max-h-12.5"}):"",n.jsx("h5",{className:"text-lg md:text-2xl",children:i})]},r))}),YL=({specData:e})=>n.jsx("div",{children:n.jsx("div",{className:"",children:e.map((t,i)=>n.jsx("div",{className:"flex capitalize odd:bg-[#F9F9F9] py-5 px-3 w-full rounded-lg",children:t.node.fields&&t.node.fields.map((r,o)=>r.key==="label_new"?n.jsx("p",{className:"text-[#717171] w-[312px]",dangerouslySetInnerHTML:{__html:r.value}},o):r.key==="value_new"?n.jsx("p",{className:"w-full",dangerouslySetInnerHTML:{__html:r.value}},o):null)},i))})}),$L=({id:e,images:t,title:i,metafields:r,variants:o,priceRange:c,handle:u,setEnquiryPopup:m,setSelectedEnquiryId:f,setSelectedEnquiryTitle:h})=>{const g=Vl(),v=async(b,T)=>{window.location.href="/products/"+T},x=async b=>{const T=JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem("myCartDetails"))||[];T.push({quantity:1,merchandiseId:b}),localStorage.setItem("myCartDetails",JSON.stringify(T)),g("/cart")};return n.jsxs("div",{className:"space-y-[26px]",children:[n.jsx("img",{src:t.edges[0].node.src,alt:"blog-thumb",className:"h-[336px] w-full object-cover"}),n.jsx("h5",{className:"font-light md:line-clamp-1",children:i}),n.jsx("span",{className:"block border-t border-[#B5B5B5] w-full"}),n.jsx("p",{className:"max-w-[345px] line-clamp-2 md:max-w-full",children:r&&r[0]&&r[0].value}),n.