 global brands to power a vast service delivery network, efficiently managing operations across 19,500+ pin codes nationwide.",bannerSlides:[{id:"fieldsupportbanner1",src:"/images/services/fieldsupport-banner-1.png",srcSm:"/images/services/fieldsupport-banner1-sm.png"},{id:"fieldsupportbanner2",src:"/images/services/fieldsupport-banner-2.png",srcSm:"/images/services/fieldsupport-banner2-sm.png"},{id:"fieldsupportbanner3",src:"/images/services/fieldsupport-banner-3.png",srcSm:"/images/services/fieldsupport-banner3-sm.png"}]},typeOfServices:[{title:"PC & Printers",iconSrc:"/images/services/pc.svg"},{title:"Server ",iconSrc:"/images/services/server.svg"},{title:"Network Devices",iconSrc:"/images/services/network-devices.png"},{title:"POS terminals",iconSrc:"/images/services/pos.svg"},{title:"Sound Box",iconSrc:"/images/services/soundbox.svg"}],whatWeDo:{tag:"What We Do",heading:"For all things electronics services from installation to break fix, parts replacement to extended warranties whether onsite or walk-in, TVSE has it covered.",dolist:[{title:"Break-Fix Services",desc:"Swift, on-site repairs with skilled technicians ensure minimal downtime and maximum uptime for IT peripherals and payment devices nationwide.",srcImg:"/images/services/fieldsupport-hwd-slide2.png"},{title:"Warranty & Support Solutions for OEMs",desc:"Comprehensive warranty management for global OEMs, covering claims processing, accurate tracking, and proactive support—enhancing customer trust while reducing operational overheads.",srcImg:"/images/services/fieldsupport-hwd-slide6.png"},{title:"Installation & Demo",desc:"As part of our warranty solutions for OEMs, we ensure seamless product installation and hands-on demos, enabling proper setup, user readiness, and a smooth customer experience.",srcImg:"/images/services/fieldsupport-hwd-slide5.png"},{title:"Inventory & Spare Parts Management ",desc:"Integrated into our warranty solutions, our efficient inventory control ensures timely replenishment, optimal utilisation, and reduced total cost of ownership (TCO).",srcImg:"/images/services/fieldsupport-hwd-slide4.png"}]},highlights:{tag:"highlights",heading:"Managing the complete electronics services lifecycle management",highlightslist:[{hightlightvalue:"19500",suffix:"+",hightlight:"Pincodes serviced"},{hightlightvalue:"637",hightlight:"Districts served"},{hightlightvalue:"320",hightlight:"Walk-in centres"},{hightlightvalue:"700",suffix:"+",hightlight:"Service partners"},{hightlightvalue:"120",suffix:"+",hightlight:"Seater call-centre"},{hightlightvalue:"5000",suffix:"+",hightlight:"Feet-on-street"}]},howWeDo:{tag:"HOW WE DO",heading:"ServiceTec Digital Platform - <br />The cornerstone of exemplary service delivery.",doList:[{title:"End-to-End Connectivity",desc:"ServiceTec seamlessly connects OEMs, consumers, repair engineers, and spare parts systems, streamlining ticket management in real-time for improved efficiency."},{title:"Efficient Service Delivery",desc:"Unified processes and workflows optimise service delivery, ensuring smooth and effective operations."},{title:"Consistent Customer Satisfaction",desc:"With advanced tools and technologies, ServiceTec delivers exceptional service quality, fostering customer satisfaction and operational consistency."}]},clientsList:["/images/logos/dell.png","/images/logos/asus.png","/images/logos/hp.png","/images/logos/acer.png","/images/logos/lenovo.png","/images/logos/tvs-elec.png","/images/logos/fiserv.png","/images/logos/hitachi.png","/images/logos/icici.png","/images/logos/razorpay.png"]},bd={heroContent:{heading:"Powering sustainability with reliable Solar  and EV charging infra solutions",desc:"Dependable operation & maintenance for Solar Energy Solutions and EV charging infrastructure backed by a trusted legacy.",bannerSlides:[{id:"greenenergybanner1",src:"/images/services/greenenergy-banner1.png",srcSm:"/images/services/greenenergy-banner1-sm.png"},{id:"greenenergybanner2",src:"/images/services/greenenergy-banner2.png",srcSm:"/images/services/greenenergy-banner2-sm.png"},{id:"greenenergybanner4",src:"/images/services/greenenergy-banner4.png",srcSm:"/images/services/greenenergy-banner4-sm.png"}]},whatWeDo:{tag:"What We Do",heading:"TVS Electronics delivers green energy solution, including operations and maintenance, thereby ensuring peak performance and sustainability.",dolist:[{title:"Comprehensive Services",desc:"Covering solar and EV charging with expert design and project management.",srcImg:"/images/services/greenenergy-hwd-slide1.png"},{title:"Efficient Solar Operations & Maintenance",desc:"Dedicated operation and maintenance solutions ensure smooth functioning and peak generation of solar energy systems.",srcImg:"/images/services/greenenergy-hwd-slide2.png"},{title:"EV Infrastructure Support",desc:"End-to-end development and management of EV charging and battery swapping stations.",srcImg:"/images/services/greenenergy-hwd-slide3.png"},{title:"Customised Solutions",desc:"Tailored services for both large-scale and distributed solar PV systems, catering to specific industry needs.",srcImg:"/images/services/greenenergy-hwd-slide4.png"},{title:"Post-Project Support",desc:"Continuous support through preventive maintenance, safety audits, and equipment repairs, ensuring long-term reliability.",srcImg:"/images/services/greenenergy-hwd-slide5.png"}]},highlights:{tag:"highlights",heading:"Delivering measurable impact for green energy projects across India.",highlightslist:[{hightlightvalue:"810",hightlight:"MW Solar Projects"},{hightlightvalue:"100",suffix:"+",hightlight:"Cities supported with brake-fix solutions"},{hightlightvalue:"20",suffix:"+",hightlight:"On-going large scale projects"},{hightlightvalue:"10",suffix:"+",hightlight:"States in India"}]},howWeDo:{tag:"HOW WE DO",heading:"Backed by the trusted TVS legacy, we deliver high-quality, reliable services tailored to the green energy sector’s unique needs.",doList:[{title:"Efficient Solar <br />Operation & Maintenance",desc:"Our O&M services include solar panel maintenance, preventive maintenance, equipment testing, and remote monitoring, guaranteeing the smooth operation of your energy systems."},{title:"EV Charging Infrastructure <br/>& Battery Swap Solutions",desc:"TVSE delivers turnkey solutions for the development of EV charging stations and battery swapping infrastructure, including installation, commissioning, and ongoing operations & maintenance support."},{title:"Brake-Fix Solutions for <br/>Distributed Solar PV Units",desc:"Providing onsite service support for solar inverters repair services, TVSE ensures quick fixes and minimises downtime."}]}},Cn={whatWeDo:{tag:"Platform-driven Excellence",headingak:"TVSE aikya",heading:" is our AI Ops platform that boosts reliability, efficiency, and user experience with AI‑driven monitoring, automation, and security—delivering 30–50% automation in the first year.",dolist:[{title:"Workplace Services",desc:"End-to-end workplace management covering desktop engineering, unified communications, and endpoint software and hardware. Focused on enhancing user experience, enabling self-service, and providing persona-based end-user management.",srcImg:"/images/services/infra-hwd-slide1.png"},{title:"Cyber Security Services",desc:"End-to-end security solutions, including risk-based vulnerability management, SOC services, and identity access control. We secure your technology landscape with proactive and reactive measures for total peace of mind.",srcImg:"/images/services/infra-hwd-slide2.png"},{title:"Digital Infra & Network Services",desc:"Comprehensive management of hybrid cloud, data centres, and networks with advanced monitoring and automation. Our proprietary Infra Management Platform ensures scalable, reliable infrastructure from NOC to application operations.",srcImg:"/images/services/infra-hwd-slide3.png"}]},whatWeDo2:{tag:"Platform-driven Excellence",heading:"TVSE aikya is our AI Ops platform that boosts reliability, efficiency, and user experience with AI‑driven monitoring, automation, and security—delivering 30–50% automation in the first year.",dolist:[{title:"Network Operations Centre (NOC) Platform",desc:"Real-time infrastructure monitoring, Proactive alerts for issue resolution, Intelligent event management for noise reduction and event co-relation, Minimizes downtime & enhances availability",srcImg:"/images/industry/DS.png"},{title:"Vulnerability & Exposure Management Platform (VEMP)",desc:"Proactively identifies vulnerabilities, Prioritizes & mitigates critical risks, Reduces cybersecurity threats",srcImg:"/images/industry/callc.png"},{title:"Security Operations Centre (SOC) Platform",desc:"AI/ML-driven threat detection & response, SIEM & SOAR-powered incident management, Increase efficiency and enhancing overall security posture",srcImg:"/images/industry/datac.png"}]},highlights:{tag:"highlights",heading:"Transform your business with TVS Electronics strategic IT Infrastructure expertise for amplified value and growth",highlightslist:[{hightlightvalue:"2",hightlight:"Centralised Network and Security Operation Centres (NOC & SOC)"},{hightlightvalue:"99.99",suffix:"%",hightlight:"Availability commitment"},{hightlightvalue:"100",suffix:"%",hightlight:"Security patch compliances"},{hightlightvalue:"150",suffix:"+",hightlight:"Seat multilingual integrated OPS control centre"}]},howWeDo:{tag:"HOW WE DO",heading:"Intelligent, intuitive and responsive operations and support that ensure sustained and uninterrupted workflow.",doList:[{title:"Eliminate Root Causes:<br/> Long-term Reliability, Fewer Repairs",desc:"Advanced data analysis eliminates repeat issues ensuring sustained performance and operational efficiency."},{title:"Maximise Availability:<br/> 99.99% Uptime, Swift Recovery",desc:"Near-100% uptime and swift recovery through proactive and predictive monitoring by our Network Operations Centre."},{title:"Enhance Risk Control:<br/> Strengthened Security, Reduced Risks",desc:"Our risk-based vulnerability management and AI-driven XDR services, aligned with the MITRE ATT&CK framework, protect against all cybersecurity risks."},{title:"Drive Continuous Improvement<br/> Automating Efficiency at Scale",desc:"Proactive problem management and an automation-first approach deliver consistent improvements and operational efficiency"},{title:"Automate and Simplify:<br/> Effortless Event Management",desc:"Our intelligent platform prioritises critical events, leveraging automation and machine learning to resolve most issues with minimal human intervention."},{title:"Customer Obsession:<br/> Holistic Protection, Integrated Solutions",desc:"Our delivery excellence framework ensures exceptional service and consistently exceeds customer expectations."}]},clientsList:["/images/logos/toyoto.png","/images/logos/itc.png","/images/logos/unichem.png","/images/logos/tvscredit.png","/images/logos/idemia.png","/images/logos/tvs-motors.png","/images/logos/tvs-capital.png"]},Ua={heroContent:{heading:"Empowering businesses with transparent auctions",desc:"India’s trusted platform for the procurement and disposal of industrial assets, offering credible digital auctions and reliable eWaste management solutions.",bannerSlides:[{id:"eauctionbanner2",src:"/images/services/eauction-banner2.png",srcSm:"/images/services/eauction-banner2-sm.png"},{id:"eauctionbanner3",src:"/images/services/eauction-banner3.png",srcSm:"/images/services/eauction-banner3-sm.png"}]},typeOfServices:[{title:"Auto Ancillary",iconSrc:"/images/logos/Auto Ancillary.svg"},{title:"Manufacturing",iconSrc:"/images/logos/manufacturing.svg"},{title:"Engineering",iconSrc:"/images/logos/engineering.svg"},{title:"Electronics",iconSrc:"/images/logos/electrical.svg"},{title:"Automobile",iconSrc:"/images/logos/automobile.svg"},{title:"Infrastructure",iconSrc:"/images/logos/infrastructure.svg"},{title:"Electrical",iconSrc:"/images/logos/electrical.svg"},{title:"Cement",iconSrc:"/images/logos/cement.svg"},{title:"Steel",iconSrc:"/images/logos/steel.svg"}],whatWeDo:{tag:"What We Do",heading:"TVSE eAuction streamlines asset transactions with cutting-edge technology, offering transparency and expert guidance for optimal business outcomes.",dolist:[{title:"Comprehensive Asset Listings",desc:"From manufacturing equipment to liquidated stock, list a wide variety of industrial assets.",srcImg:"/images/services/eauction-wwd-img1.png"},{title:"Nationwide Buyer Base",desc:"Gain access to a broad network of vetted buyers and sellers, expanding your business reach.",srcImg:"/images/services/eauction-wwd-img3.png"},{title:"User-friendly Interface",desc:"Easy registration, quick asset uploads, and fast bidding make transactions hassle-free.",srcImg:"/images/services/eauction-wwd-img2.png"},{title:"Transparent Transactions",desc:"Full visibility at every step, ensuring fair dealings for all parties involved.",srcImg:"/images/services/eauction-wwd-img7.png"},{title:"Maximised Returns",desc:"Tailored auction strategies help sellers achieve the best market price for their assets.",srcImg:"/images/services/eauction-wwd-img4.png"},{title:"Responsible eWaste Management",desc:"TVSE, as a Producer Responsibility Organisation, ensures the eco-friendly collection and management of end-of-life eWaste.",srcImg:"/images/services/eauction-wwd-img5.png"},{title:"Personalised Post-Auction Support",desc:"Dedicated support for both buyers and sellers, ensuring smooth transitions and optimal outcomes after the auction.",srcImg:"/images/services/eauction-wwd-img6.png"}]},highlights:{tag:"highlights",heading:"Trusted by businesses across industries, delivering measurable success.",highlightslist:[{hightlightvalue:"800",suffix:"+",hightlight:"Auctions held per year"},{hightlightvalue:"1000",suffix:"+ Crores",hightlight:"Worth of assets auctioned"},{hightlightvalue:"50",suffix:"+",hightlight:"Clients served"},{hightlightvalue:"25",suffix:"+",hightlight:"Years of Industry leadership"}]},howWeDo:{tag:"HOW WE DO",heading:"Dynamic pricing auctions and asset matching services that seamlessly connect industrial buyers and sellers.",doList:[{title:"Auctioning of Industrial Assets",desc:"Facilitating the sale of diverse assets through our transparent, efficient auction platform, ensuring wide exposure and the best returns."},{title:"Asset Valuation",desc:"Expert appraisal services provide you with accurate asset valuation, helping you set the right price before auctioning"},{title:"Customised Auction Events",desc:"Personalised auction solutions tailored to your industry’s needs, with the option to self-host auctions on our platform for complete control and flexibility."},{title:"End-to-End Auction Management",desc:"From asset listing to final sale, we provide full support throughout the auction process, ensuring a smooth and secure transaction experience."},{title:"Comprehensive eWaste Management for Sustainable Operations",desc:"TVSE’s end-to-end eWaste management services—from buyback and exchange programs to refurbishment, last-mile collection, and recycling—help businesses reduce costs, maximise asset value, and ensure environmentally sound disposal."}]},testimonials:{tag:"TESTIMONIALS",heading:"This is why we do, what we do!",testimonialList:[{clientName:"Plant Manager",clientImg:"/images/services/review-client-thumb.png",company:"Infrastructure Industry",review:"We have witnessed remarkable results after partnering with Auctionindia.com. Their platform brings value to our company, improving surplus management and maximizing returns."},{clientName:"Project Manager",clientImg:"/images/services/review-client-thumb.png",company:"Construction Industry",review:"Auctionindia.com has transformed our sourcing strategy. The platform provides access to surplus inventory across industries, helping us find cost-effective solutions for our projects. A game-changer for our business!"},{clientName:"Supply Chain Manager",clientImg:"/images/services/review-client-thumb.png",company:"Automobile Industry",review:"A great solution for surplus disposal! The platform's seamless interface and access to buyers in various industries ensure a hassle-free selling experience. Thanks to auctionindia.com!"}]},clientsList:["/images/logos/lgb.png","/images/logos/wabco.png","/images/logos/titan-company.png","/images/logos/ace-manufacturing.png","/images/logos/ucal-fuel-systems.png","/images/logos/schaeffler.png","/images/logos/federal-mogul.png","/images/logos/global-tvs.png","/images/logos/daikin.png","/images/logos/hmd.png","/images/logos/cg.png","/images/logos/sundaram-clayton.png","/images/logos/mep.png","/images/logos/schaeffler.png","/images/services/mi-logo.png","/images/logos/numberic.png","/images/logos/ashok-leyland.png","/images/logos/brakes-india.png","/images/logos/larsen&turbo.png","/images/logos/hcc.png","/images/logos/kennametal.png","/images/logos/tvs.png","/images/logos/tmtl.png","/images/logos/cem.png"]},vs={heroContent:{heading:"Propelling the future with cutting edge Electronic Manufacturing Services",desc:"Built on 65 acres, our factory embodies cutting-edge technology and streamlined manufacturing processes."},typeOfServices:[{title:"Automotive",iconSrc:"/images/services/automotive.svg"},{title:"EV",iconSrc:"/images/services/ev-icon.svg"},{title:"Solar",iconSrc:"/images/services/solar.svg"},{title:"Consumer electronics",iconSrc:"/images/services/electronics.svg"},{title:"IT Peripherals",iconSrc:"/images/services/it-peripherals.svg"},{title:"Industrial",iconSrc:"/images/services/industrial.svg"}],whatWeDo:{heading:"Future-ready 360° manufacturing of electronics, featuring ESD compliance, precise temperature and humidity control, and Industry 4.0 systems.",dolist:[{title:"Product Design",desc:"Comprehensive, cost-efficient solutions from initial concept to final design, tailored to your requirements."},{title:"Sourcing",desc:"Access to a global network for sourcing high-quality, reliable components."},{title:"High-Quality PCB Assembly",desc:"Precision-driven assembly using surface-mount and through-hole technologies."},{title:"Box Build Assembly",desc:"Complete system integration with rigorous testing to meet exacting quality standards."},{title:"Prototype Development",desc:"Rapid prototype development to accelerate time-to-market with functional designs."},{title:"Mass Production",desc:"Scalable, high-efficiency manufacturing leveraging advanced automation and lean methodologies."},{title:"Testing",desc:"Comprehensive ICT, FCT, and ESS testing to ensure optimal performance and durability."},{title:"Logistics",desc:"Streamlined supply chain management with efficient inventory control and real-time tracking."}]},highlights:{tag:"highlights",heading:"Experience the efficiency and reliability of a modern digital factory",highlightslist:[{id:"manufac-highlight-1",src:"/images/services/manufac-highlight-1.png",srcSm:"/images/services/manufac-highlight-1-sm.png"},{id:"manufac-highlight-2",src:"/images/services/manufac-highlight-2.png",srcSm:"/images/services/manufac-highlight-2-sm.png"},{id:"manufac-highlight-3",src:"/images/services/manufac-highlight-3.png",srcSm:"/images/services/manufac-highlight-3-sm.png"},{id:"manufac-highlight-4",src:"/images/services/manufac-highlight-4.png",srcSm:"/images/services/manufac-highlight-4-sm.png"}]},howWeDo:{tag:"HOW WE DO",heading:"Leading the way in electronic manufacturing with cutting-edge facilities",doList:[{title:"Built for Industry 4.0",desc:"TVSE’s facilities adhere to Industry 4.0 standards, integrating advanced digital technologies to deliver global-quality products for leading brands.",srcImg:"/images/services/manufac-accordion-img2.png"},{title:"Intelligent Manufacturing with MES",desc:"Powered by a state-of-the-art MES, our shop floor ensures real-time anomaly detection, end-to-end traceability, and quality compliance.",srcImg:"/images/services/manufac-accordion-img3.png"},{title:"Smart Automation for Consistency",desc:"Leveraging automation technologies like part identification and segregation, we ensure consistent, high-standard product delivery across the line.",srcImg:"/images/services/manufac-accordion-img4.png"},{title:"Seamless Integration with IoT and AI",desc:"Our assembly lines leverage IoT, Big Data, and Machine Learning, linked to cloud technology, for streamlined operations and enhanced efficiency.",srcImg:"/images/services/manufac-accordion-img5.png"},{title:"Optimising Quality with Advanced Tech",desc:"Using AOI, SPI, and X-ray systems, combined with real-time Shop Floor Control Systems (SFCS), we ensure superior quality control and optimise material tracking and labour efficiency.",srcImg:"/images/services/manufac-accordion-img6.png"}]},aboutFactory:{tag:"SUSTAINABLE FACTORY",heading:"Powered by Sustainability, Recognised for Excellence",desc:"Our factory runs entirely on renewable energy, ensuring green operations and output. Proud recipients of the SEEM Awards, we are committed to excellence in energy management and a sustainable future."}},wd={heroContent:{heading:"High-Precision Repair services for mission-critical electronics",desc:"Expert PCB & Panel Repairs for IT, Print, Data Capture, Medical & Power Electronics – Serving OEMs, Retail, Industrial, EV & Banking Sectors",bannerSlides:[{id:"repairbanner1",src:"/images/services/repair-banner-1.png",srcSm:"/images/services/repair-banner-1-sm.png"},{id:"repairbanner2",src:"/images/services/repair-banner-2.png",srcSm:"/images/services/repair-banner-2-sm.png"},{id:"repairbanner3",src:"/images/services/repair-banner-3.png",srcSm:"/images/services/repair-banner-3-sm.png"}]},typeOfServices:[{title:"OEMs",iconSrc:"/images/services/oems.svg"},{title:"Retail",iconSrc:"/images/services/retail.svg"},{title:"Industrial Automation",iconSrc:"/images/services/industry.svg"},{title:"EV",iconSrc:"/images/services/ev.svg"},{title:"Banking",iconSrc:"/images/services/banking.svg"}],whatWeDo:{tag:"What We Do",heading:"Powered by advanced diagnostics and precision tools, our 16,000 sq.ft. facili