lity",iconSrc:"/images/all-products/hospitality-icon.svg"}],S4=[{title:"What are the different types of keyboards?",desc:"Keyboards come in various types, catering to different user requirements. Some popular keyboard types include: <br/><br/> <strong>Membrane Keyboards –</strong> These keyboards use a thin membrane layer beneath the keys to register keystrokes. Membrane keyboards are affordable, lightweight, and offer a quieter typing experience.<br/><br/><strong>Mechanical Keyboards –</strong> Mechanical keyboard and mouse combos are popular among gamers and typists due to their durability, tactile feedback, and faster response time. They use individual mechanical switches under each key, providing a premium typing experience.<br/><br/><strong>Wireless Keyboards –</strong> Wireless keyboard and mouse sets offer clutter-free and convenient connectivity. These keyboards connect to your computer via Bluetooth or a USB receiver, allowing you to work without the need for cables.<br/><br/><strong>Gaming Keyboards –</strong> Gaming keyboard and mouse combos feature customizable backlighting, programmable keys, and ergonomic designs to enhance your gaming experience."},{title:"What are the different types of mice?",desc:"Just like keyboards, mice also come in various types, each designed to cater to specific user needs. Some popular mouse types include: <br/><br/>Optical Mouse– Optical mice use LED lights and sensors to track movement, offering smooth and precise cursor control. They work well on most surfaces, except for reflective or transparent ones.<br/><br/>Laser Mouse – Laser mice use infrared laser sensors for tracking, providing higher sensitivity and precision than optical mice. They work well on a wide range of surfaces, including reflective and transparent ones.<br/><br/> Wireless Mouse – Wireless mice offer a clutter-free and convenient option, connecting to your computer via Bluetooth or a USB receiver.<br/><br/>Gaming Mouse – Gaming mice feature customizable buttons, adjustable DPI settings, and ergonomic designs to enhance your gaming experience"},{title:"How to choose the right keyboard and mice?",desc:"TVS Electronics offers a vast selection of keyboards online, catering to various user requirements. Browse our collection of mechanical keyboard and mouse combos, wireless keyboards, gaming keyboard and mouse combo sets, USB keyboards, and more. Find the perfect keyboard for your needs at an attractive keyboard price.<br/><br/>Choose from top-of-the-line options, such as the Gold TVS-e mechanical keyboard and mouse, which provides exceptional durability and performance. Explore wireless mechanical keyboard options for a perfect blend of convenience and performance."},{title:"What are the combos available? ",desc:"TVS Electronics is your one-stop shop for the best keyboard and mouse combo options to suit your needs and budget. Our extensive range of keyboards & mouse includes various types, such as mechanical keyboard and mouse combos, wireless keyboard and mouse sets, gaming keyboard and mouse combos, and more. We are dedicated to providing high-quality products at competitive prices, ensuring you get the best value for your money."}],T4=()=>{const e=t=>{const i=document.getElementById(t);i&&i.scrollIntoView({behavior:"smooth"})};return S.useEffect(()=>{localStorage.setItem("productCategory","keyboards")},[]),n.jsxs("div",{children:[n.jsxs(ws,{children:[n.jsx("link",{rel:"canonical",href:"https://www.tvselectronics.in/category/keyboards"}),n.jsx("script",{type:"application/ld+json",children:`{
