ive operations."},{title:"2. Do TVS currency counters detect fake notes?",desc:"Yes. Most TVS <strong> note counting machines</strong>  come equipped with fake note detection features, such as UV, MG (magnetic), and IR sensors, to identify counterfeit currency and help prevent fraud."},{title:"3. Can TVS cash counting machines handle mixed denominations?",desc:"Select models of TVS currency counters can identify and count mixed denominations, calculate total value, and segregate notes based on denomination. This is ideal for faster and more accurate <strong> cash management</strong> ."},{title:"4. Are TVS cash counters suitable for high-volume businesses?",desc:"Absolutely. TVS <strong> cash counter machines</strong>  are built for high-speed counting and durability, making them ideal for retail outlets, banks, fuel stations, and other high-cash-volume environments."},{title:"5. What is the counting speed of TVS note counting machines?",desc:"TVS <strong> note counting machines</strong> typically offer high counting speeds ranging from 1000 to 1200 notes per minute, depending on the model. This ensures efficient processing and reduced time for <strong>cash handling</strong> ."},{title:"6. How accurate are TVS currency counting machines?",desc:"TVS <strong> currency counters</strong>  deliver highly accurate results with minimal counting errors. Models with value mode and fake note detection also ensure accuracy in denomination and authenticity checks."},{title:"7. Do the machines support new currency notes issued by the RBI?",desc:"Yes, TVS <strong> note counters</strong>  are updated to support the latest currency notes issued by the Reserve Bank of India, including ₹500, ₹200, ₹100, ₹50, ₹20, ₹10, and ₹2000 denominations (where applicable)."},{title:"8. Can I use TVS currency counters in low-light or noisy environments?",desc:"Yes. Many models are designed with bright displays and noise-optimised components, allowing easy use in various environments including dimly lit or noisy settings."},{title:"9. What is the warranty on TVS note counting machines?",desc:"TVS Electronics provides standard warranty coverage on all <strong> currency counting machines</strong> . Warranty terms may vary by model, and extended support is available through authorised service centres."},{title:"10. Where can I buy TVS cash counter machines and get service support?",desc:"You can purchase TVS cash counting machines through the <strong><a href='https://beta.tvselectronics.in/all-products/cash-counters'> official store</a></strong>, e-commerce platforms, and authorised retailers. Support for installation, maintenance, and spare parts is available via the <strong><a href='https://beta.tvselectronics.in/product-support'>TVS Product Support</a></strong> portal and service network."}],W4=()=>{const e=t=>{const i=document.getElementById(t);i&&i.scrollIntoView({behavior:"smooth"})};return S.useEffect(()=>{localStorage.setItem("productCategory","cash-counters")},[]),n.jsxs("div",{children:[n.jsxs(ws,{children:[n.jsx("link",{rel:"canonical",href:"https://www.tvselectronics.in/category/cash-counters"}),n.jsx("script",{type:"application/ld+json",children:`{
