formation”"})," is information that has been combined with information about other users and analyzed or evaluated as a whole, such that no specific individual may be reasonably identified. For example, Aggregate Information may include a statement that says “50% of our users have used the mobile app in the last month”."]}),n.jsxs("p",{children:[n.jsx("strong",{children:"“Cookies”"})," are text files, typically small in size that are placed on your computer by a web page server. Cookies cannot be used to run programs or deliver viruses to your computer. Cookies are uniquely assigned to you, and can only be read by a web server in the domain that issued the cookie to you."]}),n.jsxs("p",{children:[n.jsx("strong",{children:"“Personal Data”"})," is any information that can be used to identify you, either alone or in combination with other information. Personal Data does not include Aggregate Information or other anonymized information (including metadata) collected by TVS-E that cannot be used to identify you, even if such information was derived from your Personal Data."]}),n.jsxs("p",{children:[n.jsx("strong",{children:"“Usage Data”"})," is information about how you use the Services, such as your browser type, domains, page views, duration, and information about the device you use to access the Services."]}),n.jsxs("p",{children:[n.jsx("strong",{children:"“Web Beacons”"})," (also known as “Clear GIFs” and “Pixel Tags”) are small bits of code embedded in web pages or in emails that are used to monitor the behavior of a website user or recipient of an email."]})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"pb-20",children:[n.jsxs("p",{className:"flex items-center gap-3 pb-10 font-semibold uppercase md:pb-14 text-primary md:whitespace-nowrap",children:["COLLECTING AND USING YOUR PERSONAL DATA",n.jsx("span",{className:"hidden w-full md:block border-primary border-y"})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"space-y-6",children:[n.jsx("p",{children:"We collect Personal Data when you buy products on the Site and when we conduct marketing activities, gather feedbacks, provide customer supports, and run our business operations. The Personal Data we collect varies based upon whether you are using the Site, products sold on the Site (“Products”), or other Services."}),n.jsx("p",{children:"For the information that you provide to us during sign up or when you set up your account or profile, the information we collect may include your name, email address, telephone number, gender, date of birth, country where you reside, and other information that may help is better provide the services to you."}),n.jsx("p",{children:"We may also collect information from your use of our Service, such as how you use a particular Service. This information includes:"}),n.jsxs("ul",{className:"pl-5 space-y-2 list-disc",children:[n.jsx("li",{children:"Device-specific information. We collect device-specific information (such as your hardware model, operating system version, unique device identifiers, and mobile network information)."}),n.jsx("li",{children:"Log information. When you use our Services, we automatically collect and store certain information in server logs, such as Usage Data, usage detail and device event information (e.g., crashes, system activity, hardware settings, browser type, browser language, the date and time of your request, and referral URL.)"}),n.jsx("li",{children:"Location information. We may collect and process information about your actual location. We use various technologies to determine location, including IP address, GPS, and other sensors. For example, if our Service can provide driving direction, traffic reporting, recommendation of establishments near your location, and similar services, then we may collect your device’s real-time or compiled geographical information in order to provide such Service to you."}),n.jsx("li",{children:"Unique application numbers. Certain Services include a unique application number. This number and information about your installation (for example, the operating system type and application version number) may be sent to us at the time of installation or update."}),n.jsx("li",{children:"Information we collect when you are signed in to our Services may be associated with your account. When information is associated with your account, we treat it as personal information."})]})]})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"pb-20 space-y-6",children:[n.jsxs("p",{className:"flex items-end gap-3 pb-8 font-semibold uppercase text-primary md:whitespace-nowrap",children:["In addition to the purposes listed above,",n.jsx("br",{})," we may also use your Personal Data to:",n.jsx("span",{className:"hidden w-full mb-2 md:block border-primary border-y"})]}),n.jsxs("ul",{className:"pl-5 space-y-2 list-disc",children:[n.jsx("li",{children:"Communicate with you. Obtain your name for purposes of communicating with you and identifying you as a user of the website or product."}),n.jsx("li",{children:"Verify your identity. We may use your Personal Data to verify who you are. For example, we may verify your age or that you have obtained your parent’s or guardian’s permission to use the website or product."}),n.jsx("li",{children:"Send you marketing materials. We may send you marketing materials, such as promotional emails or catalogue, to keep you informed of our upcoming product releases. You generally must opt-in to receiving our marketing materials, and you may opt out of receiving them at any time. For more information on how to opt out, please see YOUR CHOICES below."}),n.jsx("li",{children:"Respond to your questions and fulfill your requests. We may send you communications upon your request or otherwise with your consent."}),n.jsx("li",{children:"Provide support and receive feedback. We may request Personal Data in order to provide support to you. We may also collect Personal Data that are associated with your feedback."})]}),n.jsx("p",{children:"We also gather non-descriptive, non-identifiable statistical information about how many visitors use our Services, how our users use the Services, how our users access certain content available on our Services, how long our users access certain content, what content our users are accessing, and our user preferences or settings for certain Services. We use this Aggregated Information for statistical analysis of how users make use of the Services so we can better improve our Services."})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"pb-20 space-y-6",children:[n.jsxs("p",{className:"flex items-end gap-3 pb-8 font-semibold uppercase text-primary md:whitespace-nowrap",children:["DATA COLLECTION TECHNOLOGIES",n.jsx("span",{className:"hidden w-full mb-2 md:block border-primary border-y"})]}),n.jsx("p",{children:"We use Cookies, Web Beacons, and other data collection technologies (together, “Data Collection Technologies”) to provide you with a better experience when you use the Services. Data Collection Technologies help you log onto the Services, remember your settings and preferences, help us keep your information safe and secure, and enable our partners to serve ads for the Products and services, including those targeted to your interests. While the Data Collection Technologies we use may change from time to time, they generally fall into the following categories:"}),n.jsxs("ul",{className:"pl-5 space-y-2 list-disc",children:[n.jsx("li",{children:"Authentication. We use cookies to verify your account and determine when you’re logged in so we can make it easier for you to access the Services and show you the appropriate experience and features."}),n.jsxs("li",{children:["Security and product integrity. We use cookies to help us keep your account and information safe and secure."," "]}),n.jsx("li",{children:"We also use cookies to combat activity that violates our policies or otherwise degrades our ability to provide our Services."}),n.jsx("li",{children:"Advertising, insights and measurement. We use cookies to help us show ads for businesses and other organizations to people who may be interested in the Products, services or causes they promote. We also use cookies to help measure the performance of ad campaigns for businesses that use the Services. Cookies help us serve and measure ads across different browsers and devices used by the same person."}),n.jsx("li",{children:"Site features and services. We use cookies to enable the functionality that helps us provide the Services and provide you with the best experience possible, including to help provide you with content relevant to your locale."}),n.jsxs("li",{children:["Analytic and research: We use Cookies to better understand how people use the website so that we can improve the Services. For example, we partner with Google Analytic, which uses Cookies to track your interactions with our Services. Google then collects that information and reports it to us, without identifying individual users. This information helps us improve our Services so that we can better serve users like you. For more information on Google Analytic, visit"," ",n.jsx(ue,{to:"https://support.google.com/analytics.",target:"_blank",className:"underline",children:"https://support.google.com/analytics."})]})]})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"space-y-6",children:[n.jsxs("p",{className:"flex items-end gap-3 pb-8 font-semibold uppercase text-primary md:whitespace-nowrap",children:["SHARING YOUR PERSONAL DATA",n.jsx("span",{className:"hidden w-full mb-2 md:block border-primary border-y"})]}),n.jsx("p",{children:"Because we know your Personal Data is important to you, we may share your information for the reason(s) disclosed to you at the time we collect it, with your consent, as well as in the following ways:"}),n.jsxs("ul",{className:"pl-5 space-y-2 list-disc",children:[n.jsx("li",{children:"At your direction. We will share your information with third parties if and when you direct us to. For example, you may ask us to share your Personal Data when you wish to interact with other users or post certain information on social media."}),n.jsx("li",{children:"With our Vendors. We may share your Personal Data with our Vendors as necessary to enable them to provide services to us. Vendors are third parties (other companies and individuals) that support the operation and maintenance of our Services."}),n.jsx("li",{children:"With our Partners. We may allow certain third parties, such as car manufacturers or electronic consumer device manufacturers, to integrate components of our Services into their own devices and software. These third parties will use our platform to access your information to facilitate our Services on their device or software. They may elect to collect or use your information using our platform without our knowledge. These third parties are separately responsible for their own privacy policies and practices. In addition, we may collect information about these third party devices or software that you use to help us provide core functions of our Services."}),n.jsx("li",{children:"With our commonly owned entities. We may share your Personal Data with other companies under common ownership and control of TVS-E, which may include our subsidiaries, corporate parent, or any other subsidiaries owned by our corporate parent. We do this in order to provide you better service and improve your experience."}),n.jsx("li",{children:"For legal purposes. We may share your Personal Data as reasonably necessary to comply with law or a legal process (including a court or government order or subpoena), to detect, prevent, or otherwise address fraud, security or technical issues, to enforce this Privacy Statement and/or the Terms of Use, and to protect the rights, property or safety of TVS-E, our users, and/or the public."}),n.jsx("li",{children:"During a corporate transaction. If TVS-E is involved in a merger, acquisition, financing, or sale of business or assets, information collected from and about users may be transferred to one or more third parties involved in such transaction and, upon such transfer, the relevant third party privacy policy or policies may govern further use of the information."}),n.jsx("li",{children:"With third party service providers: We may disclose or share your personal information with our customer support centre, an authorized repairer or third party service providers whom we work with in the course of our business including customer support, security, financial and legal advisory, banking, credit reporting, fraud checks, data storage, information processing, marketing, product reviews, responding to customer queries and complaints, technology services or law enforcement agency for compliance purposes or to assist with investigations."})]})]})]})]}),Q4=()=>n.jsxs("div",{children:[n.jsxs("div",{className:"relative text-white bg-primary-bg pt-25 lg:pt-36",children:[n.jsx("img",{src:"/images/workforce/directors-spiral-up.svg",alt:"sprial bg",className:"absolute right-0 top-10 w-46 md:w-auto"}),n.jsx("img",{src:"/images/workforce/directors-spiral-down.svg",alt:"sprial bg",className:"absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-46 md:w-auto"}),n.jsx("div",{className:"container",children:n.jsxs("h1",{className:"font-[350] text-4xl md:text-[56px] md:leading-[62px] text-center py-40",children:["Returns & ",n.jsx("br",{className:"sm:hidden"}),"Refund Policy"]})})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"mx-auto max-w-4xl py-30 px-5 font-[350]",children:[n.jsxs("div",{className:"pb-20 space-y-6",children:[n.jsxs("p",{className:"flex items-center gap-3 pb-8 font-semibold uppercase text-primary md:whitespace-nowrap",children:["Return period",n.jsx("span",{className:"hidden w-full md:block border-primary border-y"})]}),n.jsx("p",{children:"The TVSE Online Store will accept returns request within  48hrs  day after delivery  date for the products in case of Transit damaged or in DOA case only."}),n.jsx("p",{children:"Please contact TVS-E Online Store contact: +91 93459 52172, speak to our customer"}),n.jsx("p",{children:"Service staff who will advise on the refund process."})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"pb-20 space-y-6",children:[n.jsxs("p",{className:"flex items-center gap-3 pb-8 font-semibold uppercase text-primary md:whitespace-nowrap",children:["Exchange/ refund conditions:",n.jsx("span",{className:"hidden w-full md:block border-primary border-y"})]}),n.jsx("p",{children:"Damaged products or Deficient on Arrival: Free replacement within 20 days remarks must be available in POD to claim replacement."}),n.jsx("p",{children:"Product failure within the warranty period contact Call Center: 08162214600 to resolve the issue"}),n.jsx("p",{children:"Order cancellation after placing order is not possible. Please clearly check and  place  the order carefully"})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"space-y-6",children:[n.jsxs("p",{className:"flex items-center gap-3 pb-8 font-semibold uppercase text-primary md:whitespace-nowrap",children:["Refunds",n.jsx("span",{className:"hidden w-full md:block border-primary border-y"})]}),n.jsx("p",{children:"Tax (if applicable) is refunded with returns."}),n.jsx("p",{children:"Original shipping and handling charges aren't refunded."}),n.jsx("p",{children:"If the payment was by Credit/Debit card or Net-Banking, we will refund the money in your Credit/Debit Card or Net-Banking account."}),n.jsx("p",{children:"Typically refunds are processed in between 7-21 working days for credit cards and 5-7 working days for debit card and net banking orders."})]})]})]}),J4=()=>n.jsxs("div",{children:[n.jsxs("div",{className:"relative text-white bg-primary-bg pt-25 lg:pt-36",children:[n.jsx("img",{src:"/images/workforce/directors-spiral-up.svg",alt:"sprial bg",className:"absolute right-0 top-10 w-46 md:w-auto"}),n.jsx("img",{src:"/images/workforce/directors-spiral-down.svg",alt:"sprial bg",className:"absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-46 md:w-auto"}),n.jsx("div",{className:"container",children:n.jsxs("h1",{className:"font-[350] text-4xl md:text-[56px] md:leading-[62px] text-center py-40",children:["Shipping & ",n.jsx("br",{className:"sm:hidden"}),"Delivery Policy"]})})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"mx-auto max-w-4xl py-20 md:py-30 px-5 font-[350]",children:[n.jsxs("div",{className:"pb-20 space-y-6",children:[n.jsx("p",{children:"Learn for free"}),n.jsx("p",{children:"TVS-E Electronics ('Company') will do everything possible to ensure Products are delivered after placing the order. This is subject to availability of the product(s) and successful payment."}),n.jsx("p",{children:"By placing an order on the website, you agree not to hold the Company responsible or legally liable for any delay in delivery that is caused by circumstances beyond the control of the Company."}),n.jsx("p",{children:"The Company offers free shipping for orders placed in the website and this shipping cost may pass on the to the customer in  future and subject to  change based on the Management decision"}),n.jsx("p",{children:"If you would like products to be delivered to more than one shipping address, please place separate orders corresponding to each of the addresses."}),n.jsx("p",{children:"Due to varying item availability, orders containing multiple items may sometimes be shipped separately. Each shipment will have its own individual tracking number, which can be tracked on the Track Order page under the same order number"})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"pb-20 space-y-6",children:[n.jsxs("p",{className:"flex items-center gap-3 pb-8 font-semibold uppercase text-primary md:whitespace-nowrap",children:["Does TVS-E Electronics ship to my address?",n.jsx("span",{className:"hidden w-full md:block border-primary border-y"})]}),n.jsx("p",{children:"Add the product(s) you want to order to the shipping cart. Go to 'My Cart' and click the 'Checkout' button. Under 'ZIP/Postal Code' look for your PIN Code (e.g. 500001). If your PIN Code is not listed, it means we do not ship to your area at this time. However, you can provide an alternative shipping address belonging to an area serviced by us."})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"space-y-6",children:[n.jsxs("p",{className:"flex items-center gap-3 pb-8 font-semibold uppercase text-primary md:whitespace-nowrap",children:["How does TVS-E Electronics fulfill orders?",n.jsx("span",{className:"hidden w-full md:block border-primary border-y"})]}),n.jsx("p",{children:"Once the order is placed you will be intimated with Email or SMS. We are working to get your orders delivered across as soon as possible."}),n.jsx("p",{children:"Orders are fulfilled by the Company in collaboration with third-party courier & cargo companies."}),n.jsx("p",{children:"Currently, due to overwhelming demand, orders placed with Standard Delivery TAT of delivering as soon as Possible with help of Premium couriers .Once the docket details is updated delivery TAT starts for your reference. For delivery timeline, please click the on the docket number in respective Transport Portal for tracking the shipment."}),n.jsx("p",{children:"Our delivery partners will attempt to complete your delivery twice before the item is returned to our warehouse. Please ensure that you provide a valid mobile number and shipping address while placing your order."}),n.jsx("p",{children:"Our delivery partners may sometimes require a valid ID proof for delivering your package. if you have any further queries. Please contact us at s.karthick@tvs-e.in"})]})]})]}),e6=()=>n.jsxs("div",{children:[n.jsxs("div",{className:"relative text-white bg-primary-bg pt-25 lg:pt-36",children:[n.jsx("img",{src:"/images/workforce/directors-spiral-up.svg",alt:"sprial bg",className:"absolute right-0 top-10 w-46 md:w-auto"}),n.jsx("img",{src:"/images/workforce/directors-spiral-down.svg",alt:"sprial bg",className:"absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-46 md:w-auto"}),n.jsx("div",{className:"container",children:n.jsx("h1",{className:"font-[350] text-4xl md:text-[56px] md:leading-[62px] text-center py-40",children:"Terms of service"})})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"mx-auto max-w-4xl py-20 md:py-30 px-5 font-[350]",children:[n.jsxs("div",{className:"pb-20 space-y-6",children:[n.jsx("p",{children:'In these Terms, references to "you", "User" shall mean the end user accessing the Website, its contents and using the Services offered through the Website. "Service Providers" mean independent third party service providers, and "we", "us" and "our" shall mean “TVS-E India Private Limited”, its franchiser, affiliates and partners.'}),n.jsx("p",{children:"By visiting our site and/ or purchasing something from us, you engage in our “Service” and agree to be bound by the following terms and conditions (“Terms & Conditions”, “Terms”), including those additional terms and conditions and policies referenced herein and/or available. These Terms & Conditions apply to all users of the site, including without limitation users who are browsers, vendors, customers, merchants etc."}),n.jsx("p",{children:"Please read these Terms & Conditions carefully before accessing or using our website. By accessing or using any part of the site, you agree to be bound by these Terms & Conditions. If you do not agree to all the terms and conditions of this agreement, then you may not access the website or use any services. If these Terms & Conditions are considered an offer, acceptance is expressly limited to these Terms & Conditions."}),n.jsx("p",{children:"Any new products which are added to the current store shall also be subject to the Terms & Conditions. You can review the most current version of the Terms & Conditions at any time on this page. We reserve the right to update, change or replace any part of these Terms & Conditions by posting updates and/or changes to our website. It is your responsibility to check this page periodically for changes. Your continued use of or access to the website following the posting of any changes constitutes acceptance of those changes."}),n.jsx("p",{children:"By agreeing to these Terms & Conditions, you represent that you are at least the age of majority in your state or province of residence, or that you are the age of majority [i.e., 18+] and you have given us your consent to allow any of your minor dependents to use this site. You may not use our products for any illegal or unauthorized purpose nor may you, in the use of the Service, violate any laws in India (including but not limited to copyright laws)."}),n.jsx("p",{children:"The headings used in this agreement are included for convenience only and will not limit or otherwise affect these Terms"})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"pb-20 space-y-6",children:[n.jsxs("p",{className:"flex items-center gap-3 pb-8 font-semibold uppercase text-primary md:whitespace-nowrap",children:["Return period",n.jsx("span",{className:"hidden w-full md:block border-primary border-y"})]}),n.jsx("p",{children:"We reserve the right to refuse service to anyone for any reason at any time. You understand that your content (not including payment details), may be transferred unencrypted and involve (a) transmissions over various networks; and (b) changes to conform and adapt to technical requirements of connecting networks or devices. Payment details are always encrypted during transfer over networks. You agree not to reproduce, duplicate, copy, sell, resell or exploit any portion of the Service, use of the Service, or access to the Service or any contact on the website through which the service is provided, without express written permission by us."})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"pb-20 space-y-6",children:[n.jsxs("p",{className:"flex items-center gap-3 pb-8 font-semibold uppercase text-primary md:whitespace-nowrap",children:["Accuracy, Completeness And ",n.jsx("br",{}),"Timeliness Of Information",n.jsx("span",{className:"hidden w-full md:block border-primary border-y"})]}),n.jsx("p",{children:"We are not responsible if information made available on this site is not accurate, complete or current. The material on this site is provided for general information only and should not be relied upon or used as the sole basis for making decisions without consulting primary, more accurate, more complete or more timely sources of information. Any reliance on the material on this site is at your own risk."}),n.jsx("p",{children:"This site may contain certain historical information. Historical information, necessarily, is not current and is provided for your reference only. We reserve the right to modify the contents of this site at any time, but we have no obligation to update any information on our site. You agree that it is your responsibility to monitor changes to our site."})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"pb-20 space-y-6",children:[n.jsxs("p",{className:"flex items-center gap-3 pb-8 font-semibold uppercase text-primary md:whitespace-nowrap",children:["Modifications To The Service And Prices",n.jsx("span",{className:"hidden w-full md:block border-primary border-y"})]}),n.jsx("p",{children:"Prices for our products are subject to change without notice. We reserve the right at any time to modify or discontinue the Service (or any part or content thereof) without notice at any time. We shall not be liable to you or to any third-party for any modification, price change, suspension or discontinuance of the Service."})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"pb-20 space-y-6",children:[n.jsxs("p",{className:"flex items-center gap-3 pb-8 font-semibold uppercase text-primary md:whitespace-nowrap",children:["Products Or Services (If Applicable)",n.jsx("span",{className:"hidden w-full md:block border-primary border-y"})]}),n.jsx("p",{children:"Certain products or services may be available exclusively online through the website. These products or services may have limited quantities and are subject to return or exchange only as per our Return Policy."}),n.jsx("p",{children:"We have made every effort to display as accurately as possible the colosur and images of our products that appear at the store."}),n.jsx("p",{children:"We cannot guarantee that your computer monitor's display of any colour will be accurate. We reserve the right but are not obligated, to limit the sales of our products or Services to any person, geographic region or jurisdiction. We may exercise this right on a case-by-case basis. We reserve the right to limit the quantities of any products or services that we offer. All descriptions of products or product pricing are subject to change at any time without notice, at the sole discretion of us. We reserve the right to discontinue any product at any time."}),n.jsx("p",{children:"Any offer for any product or service made on this site is void where prohibited. We do not warrant that the quality of any products, services, information, or other material purchased or obtained by you will meet your expectations."})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"pb-20 space-y-6",children:[n.jsxs("p",{className:"flex items-center gap-3 pb-8 font-semibold uppercase text-primary md:whitespace-nowrap",children:["Accuracy Of Billing And",n.jsx("br",{})," Account Information",n.jsx("span",{className:"hidden w-full md:block border-primary border-y"})]}),n.jsx("p",{children:"We reserve the right to refuse any order you place with us. We may, in our sole discretion, limit or cancel quantities purchased per person, per household or per order. These restrictions may include orders placed by or under the same customer account, the same credit card, debit card ,UPI, wallet payment, Net banking ,any other modes of payment available and/or orders that use the same billing and/or shipping address. In the event that we make a change to or cancel an order, we may attempt to notify you by contacting the e-mail and/or billing address/phone number provided at the time the order was made. We reserve the right to limit or prohibit orders that, in our sole judgment, appear to be placed by dealers, resellers or distributors."}),n.jsx("p",{children:"You agree to provide current, complete and accurate purchase and account information for all purchases made at our store. You agree to promptly update your account and other information, including your email address and payment details and expiration dates so that we can complete your transactions and contact you as needed. For more detail, please review our Returns Policy."})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"pb-20 space-y-6",children:[n.jsxs("p",{className:"flex items-center gap-3 pb-8 font-semibold uppercase text-primary md:whitespace-nowrap",children:["User Comments, Feedback ",n.jsx("br",{}),"And Other Submissions",n.jsx("span",{className:"hidden w-full md:block border-primary border-y"})]}),n.jsx("p",{children:"If, at our request, you send certain specific submissions (for example contest entries) or without a request from us you send creative ideas, suggestions, proposals, plans, or other materials, whether online, by email, by postal mail, or otherwise (collectively, 'comments'), you agree that we may, at any time, without restriction, edit, copy, publish, distribute, translate and otherwise use in any medium any comments that you forward to us. We are and shall be under no obligation (1) to maintain any comments in confidence; (2) to pay compensation for any comments; or (3) to respond to any comments."}),n.jsx("p",{children:"We may, but have no obligation to, monitor, edit or remove content that we determine in our sole discretion are unlawful, offensive, threatening, defamatory, pornographic, obscene or otherwise objectionable or violates any party’s intellectual property or these Terms & Conditions."}),n.jsx("p",{children:"You agree that your comments will not violate any right of any third-party, including copyright, trademark, privacy, personality or other personal or proprietary right. You further agree that your comments will not contain unlawful, abusive or obscene material, or contain any computer virus or other malware that could in any way affect the operation of the Service or any related website. You may not use a false e-mail address, pretend to be someone other than yourself, or otherwise mislead us or third-parties as to the origin of any comments. You are solely responsible for any comments you make and their accuracy. We take no responsibility and assume no liability for any comments posted by you or any third-party."})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"pb-20 space-y-6",children:[n.jsxs("p",{className:"flex items-center gap-3 pb-8 font-semibold uppercase text-primary md:whitespace-nowrap",children:["Personal Information privacy policy",n.jsx("span",{className:"hidden w-full md:block border-primary border-y"})]}),n.jsx("p",{children:"Your submission of personal information through the store is governed by our Privacy Policy. To view our Privacy Policy please visit privacy policy."})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"pb-20 space-y-6",children:[n.jsxs("p",{className:"flex items-center gap-3 pb-8 font-semibold uppercase text-primary md:whitespace-nowrap",children:["Errors, Inaccuracies And Omissions",n.jsx("span",{className:"hidden w-full md:block border-primary border-y"})]}),n.jsx("p",{children:"Occasionally there may be information on our site or in the Service that contains typographical errors, inaccuracies or omissions that may relate to product descriptions, pricing, promotions, offers, product shipping charges, transit times and availability. We reserve the right to correct any errors, inaccuracies or omissions, and to change or update information or cancel orders if any information in the Service or on any related website is inaccurate at any time without prior notice (including after you have submitted your order).We undertake no obligation to update, amend or clarify information in the Service or on any related website, including without limitation, pricing information, except as required by law. No specified update or refresh date applied in the Service or on any related website, should be taken to indicate that all information in the Service or on any related website has been modified or updated."})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"pb-20 space-y-6",children:[n.jsxs("p",{className:"flex items-center gap-3 pb-8 font-semibold uppercase text-primary md:whitespace-nowrap",children:["Prohibited Uses",n.jsx("span",{className:"hidden w-full md:block border-primary border-y"})]}),n.jsx("p",{children:"In addition to other prohibitions as set forth in the Terms & Conditions, you are prohibited from using the site or its content: (a) for any unlawful purpose; (b) to solicit others to perform or participate in any unlawful acts; (c) to violate any international, federal, provincial or state regulations, rules, laws, or local ordinances; (d) to infringe upon or violate our intellectual property rights or the intellectual property rights of others; (e) to harass, abuse, insult, harm, defame, slander, disparage, intimidate, or discriminate based on gender, sexual orientation, religion, ethnicity, race, age, national origin, or disability; (f) to submit false or misleading information; (g) to upload or transmit viruses or any other type of malicious code that will or may be used in any way that will affect the functionality or operation of the Service or of any related website, other websites, or the Internet; (h) to collect or track the personal information of others; (i) to spam, phish, pharm, pretext, spider, crawl, or scrape; (j) for any obscene or immoral purpose; or (k) to interfere with or circumvent the security features of the Service or any related website, other websites, or the Internet. We reserve the right to terminate your use of the Service or any related website for violating any of the prohibited uses."}),n.jsx("p",{})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"space-y-6",children:[n.jsxs("p",{className:"flex items-center gap-3 pb-8 font-semibold uppercase text-primary md:whitespace-nowrap",children:["Trademark, Copyright and Restriction",n.jsx("span",{className:"hidden w-full md:block border-primary border-y"})]}),n.jsx("p",{children:"This site is controlled and operated by TVS-E . All material on this site, including images, illustrations, audio clips, and video clips, are protected by copyrights, trademarks, and other intellectual property rights. Material on Website is solely for your personal, non-commercial use. You must not copy, reproduce, republish, upload, post, transmit or distribute such material in any way, including by email or other electronic means and whether directly or indirectly and you must not assist any other person to do so. Without the prior written consent of TVS-E , modification of the materials, use of the materials on any other website or networked computer environment or use of the materials for any purpose other than personal, non-commercial use is a violation of the copyrights, trademarks and other proprietary rights, and is prohibited. Any use for which You receive any remuneration, whether in money or otherwise, is a commercial use for the purposes of this clause"})]})]})]}),t6=()=>n.jsxs("div",{children:[n.jsxs("div",{className:"relative text-white bg-primary-bg pt-25 lg:pt-36",children:[n.jsx("img",{src:"/images/workforce/directors-spiral-up.svg",alt:"sprial bg",className:"absolute right-0 top-10 w-46 md:w-auto"}),n.jsx("img",{src:"/images/workforce/directors-spiral-down.svg",alt:"sprial bg",className:"absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-46 md:w-auto"}),n.jsx("div",{className:"container",children:n.jsxs("h1",{className:"font-[350] text-4xl md:text-[56px] md:leading-[62px] text-center py-40",children:["Extended Warranty ",n.jsx("br",{}),"Terms and Conditions"]})})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"mx-auto max-w-4xl py-20 md:py-30 px-5 font-[350]",children:[n.jsxs("div",{className:"pb-20 space-y-6",children:[n.jsxs("p",{className:"flex items-center gap-3 pb-8 font-semibold uppercase text-primary whitespace-nowrap",children:["Extended Warranty Protection",n.jsx("span",{className:"hidden w-full md:block border-primary border-y"})]}),n.jsx("p",{children:"TVS-E Extended Warranty Protection (EWP) pack allows you to protect your devices beyond the default warranty period. Owning an Extended Warranty is a smart way to be reliable of a longer service assurance for your product and peace of mind for you."})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"pb-20 space-y-6",children:[n.jsxs("p",{className:"flex items-center gap-3 pb-8 font-semibold uppercase text-primary md:whitespace-nowrap",children:["Why Choose TVS-E ?",n.jsx("span",{className:"hidden w-full md:block border-primary border-y"})]}),n.jsx("p",{children:"Following the expiry of your product’s default warranty, servicing a product comes with a set of difficulties. Paying for every repair at different occasions, in addition to being charged on the higher side for spare parts can be burdensome. Besides, a repair through an inexperienced third party vendor or an unauthorised engineer might lead to damaging your product. With TVS-E Extended Warranty Protection (EWP) Plans, you are free from all those worries."}),n.jsx("p",{children:"The EWP packs are priced at a nominal price, so that TVS-E customers can continue to benefit from quality service through qualified TVS-E engineers, thus ensuring uncompromised functionality of your product."}),n.jsx("p",{children:"This EWP plan is designed based on the understanding of customer’s practical needs. Thus, bringing you the assurance of ‘TVS quality’ and commitment towards the repair of your products. All EWP offerings are genuinely consumer oriented in their approach."})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"pb-20 space-y-6",children:[n.jsxs("p",{className:"flex items-center gap-3 pb-8 font-semibold uppercase text-primary md:whitespace-nowrap",children:["Activation",n.jsx("span",{className:"hidden w-full md:block border-primary border-y"})]}),n.jsxs("p",{children:["Quality service by authorised personnel",n.jsx("br",{}),"Value for money",n.jsx("br",{}),"Major parts of the product are covered",n.jsx("br",{}),"Increased product life period",n.jsx("br",{}),"Continuous service standards",n.jsx("br",{}),"Door step service for eligible products"]})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"pb-20 space-y-6",children:[n.jsxs("p",{className:"flex items-center gap-3 pb-8 font-semibold uppercase text-primary md:whitespace-nowrap",children:["How It Works",n.jsx("span",{className:"hidden w-full md:block border-primary border-y"})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"space-y-6",children:[n.jsx("span",{children:n.jsx("strong",{children:"Activation:"})}),n.jsx("p",{children:"A process that is designed to be hassle free for the customer."}),n.jsx("p",{children:"Upon choosing the product, fill in your personal and product details. If your product is eligible for EWP, you are automatically directed to the payment gateway. Post payment, you shall receive your order confirmation via mail. The invoice copy shall be mailed to you in three working days."})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"space-y-6",children:[n.jsx("span",{children:n.jsx("strong",{children:"Who can buy:"})}),n.jsx("p",{children:"Extended Warranty Packs are eligible only for retail customers owning less than 5 products of the same model."})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"space-y-6",children:[n.jsx("span",{children:n.jsx("strong",{children:"EWP Activation Date:"})}),n.jsx("p",{children:"Your EWP starts from the date of expiry of manufacturer’s warranty."})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"space-y-6",children:[n.jsx("span",{children:n.jsx("strong",{children:"When can you avail the service?"})}),n.jsx("p",{children:"EWP needs to be purchased within 90 days of product’s purchase date."})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"space-y-6",children:[n.jsx("span",{children:n.jsx("strong",{children:"Post- Purchase Service:"})}),n.jsx("p",{children:"Reach us on any of the below service lines. Our engineer will be at your service to resolve your product’s issue and put it back in working condition."})]}),n.jsxs("div",{className:"space-y-6",children:[n.jsx("span",{children:n.jsx("strong",{children:"Post- Purchase Service:"})}),n.jsxs("p",{children:["Call: 1860 425 2078 / +91 816 2214600",n.jsx("br",{}),"Mail: support@tvs-e.in",n.jsx("br",{}),"Whatsapp: 08124030088",n.jsx("br",{}),'SMS: 8