s, and logistics companies across India.",srcImg:"/images/industry/industry-wwd-slide5.png"}]},bfsi:{tag:"BFSI",heading:"Secure and Reliable Solutions for the BFSI Sector",desc:"From secure printing to dependable peripherals, TVSE provides solutions that ensure smooth operations for modern banking and financial institutions.",accordImg:"/images/industry/bfsi-image.png",dolist:[{title:"Specialty Printers",desc:"Secure printing for passbooks and other banking assets."},{title:"Track and Trace Products",desc:"Precision tools for asset tracking."},{title:"Peripherals",desc:"Reliable keyboards, mice, and dot matrix printers designed for banking environments."}]},logistics:{tag:"Logistics",heading:"Pioneering Track and Trace Solutions for Logistics",desc:"TVSE delivers industry-leading barcode scanners, label printers, and handheld terminals to streamline logistics operations.",accordImg:"/images/industry/logistics-img.png",dolist:[{title:"Barcode Scanners",desc:"Fast and accurate scanning for shipping and tracking."},{title:"Label Printers",desc:"Quick identification marking for packages and parcels."},{title:"Handheld Terminals",desc:"Efficient tools for on-the-go data capture and processing."}]},sector:{tag:"Government / Public Sector",heading:"Partners in innovation, <br/>driving progress for the greater good",desc:"TVSE is a trusted partner for government bodies, providing custom-built solutions that enhance operational efficiency across various public services.",sectorlist:[{sectorName:"Indian Railways",shortDesc:"Automated Train Guard Manual and meal management solutions.",thumbnail:"/images/industry/indianrailways.png",targetRoute:"#"},{sectorName:"State Transport",shortDesc:"Portable ticketing solutions integrating hardware and software.",thumbnail:"/images/industry/statetransport.png",targetRoute:"#"},{sectorName:"Chennai Metro",shortDesc:"QR code-based ticketing systems for faster passenger flow.",thumbnail:"/images/industry/chennaimetro.png",targetRoute:"#"}]}},wi={heroContent:{heading:"Empowering Retail with reliable hardware and software solutions",desc:"TVSE is your single point solution provider for retail businesses of all sizes, offering comprehensive hardware and billing software to streamline operations and enhance customer experiences.",bannerSlides:[{id:"industrybanner1",src:"/images/industry/retail-banner-1.png",srcSm:"/images/industry/retail-banner1-sm.png"},{id:"industrybanner2",src:"/images/industry/retail-banner-2.png",srcSm:"/images/industry/retail-banner2-sm.png"},{id:"industrybanner3",src:"/images/industry/retail-banner-3.png",srcSm:"/images/industry/retail-banner3-sm.png"}]},whatWeDo:{tag:"What We Do",heading:"TVSE offers robust hardware and billing software solutions to help retail businesses optimise their operations, from seamless transactions at the counter to efficient back-office management.",dolist:[{title:"Reliable Performance",desc:"Tailored services that integrate hardware and software.",srcImg:"/images/industry/retail-wwd-slide1.png"},{title:"Seamless Integration",desc:"Enhanced onsite industry solutions ensure prompt dispatch, skilled technicians, and comprehensive support, maximising equipment uptime and customer satisfaction unified across the country.",srcImg:"/images/industry/retail-wwd-slide2.png"},{title:"Cost-Effective",desc:"With global reach and local expertise, the walk-in centers provide prompt diagnosis, expert repairs, and personalised support, ensuring an excellent service experience for customers.",srcImg:"/images/industry/retail-wwd-slide3.png"},{title:"Comprehensive Support",desc:"Clear and efficient warranty management solutions covering claim processing, accurate tracking, and proactive support, enhancing customer trust and satisfaction while reducing overheads.",srcImg:"/images/industry/retail-wwd-slide4.png"},{title:"Trusted TVS Legacy",desc:"Giving the customers a seamless installation and insightful demos for the brand. TVSE ensures meticulous setup, comprehensive training, and exceptional customer satisfaction, setting the stage for product success.",srcImg:"/images/industry/retail-wwd-slide5.png"}]},ourProducts:{tag:"Our Products",heading:"The Right tools for efficient Retail",products:[{targetRoute:"/category/printers",imgSrc:"/images/industry/retail-printers.png"},{targetRoute:"/category/touch-pos",imgSrc:"/images/industry/retail-touchpos.png"},{targetRoute:"/category/scanners",imgSrc:"/images/industry/retail-scanners.png"},{targetRoute:"/category/keyboards",imgSrc:"/images/industry/retail-keyboards.png"}]},billingsolutions:{tag:"BILLING SOLUTIONS",heading:"Faster checkouts are now a reality",solutionsList:[{title:"TVSE PAY:",desc:"Streamline your retail operations with TVSePAY, a user-friendly billing app designed for SMEs to simplify transactions and boost profitability.",iconImg:"/images/industry/tvse-pay-icon.svg"},{title:"Royal POS:",desc:"A cloud-based, device-friendly POS for restaurants and retail, offering inventory control, outlet management, and delivery integration.",iconImg:"/images/industry/royalpos-icon.svg"},{title:"SnapBizz:",desc:"SnapBizz turns Kirana stores into virtual supermarkets, boosting profitability by 20-25% with secure, cloud-based technology.",iconImg:"/images/industry/snapbizz-icon.svg"},{title:"QueueBuster:",desc:"Supercharge your retail business with our versatile app, streamlining operations and boosting sales for stores, restaurants, boutiques, and warehouses.",iconImg:"/images/industry/queuebuster-icon.svg"}]},segments:{tag:"SEGMENTS",heading:"Proven Solutions for Retail Success",desc:"TVSE solutions are trusted by a wide range of retail businesses, from small independent shops to larger chains, ensuring smooth operations and enhanced customer experiences.",segmentList:[{title:"Neighbourhood Stores",desc:"POS systems that handle everyday retail challenges with speed and accuracy.",srcImg:"/images/industry/neighbourhoodstores.png"},{title:"Supermarkets",desc:"Scalable billing software that supports high transaction volumes and integrates with inventory management.",srcImg:"/images/industry/supermarkets.png"},{title:"Speciality Retailers",desc:"Customisable solutions tailored to the unique needs of niche markets.",srcImg:"/images/industry/speciality-retailers.png"},{title:"QSR",desc:"Streamline fast-paced orders and billing with efficient, user-friendly solutions tailored for quick service restaurants.",srcImg:"/images/industry/qsr.png"},{title:"Pharmacy",desc:"Ensure accurate billing, inventory tracking, and regulatory compliance with reliable pharmacy management tools.",srcImg:"/images/industry/pharmacy.png"},{title:"Textiles",desc:"Simplify inventory management and streamline billing to meet the unique demands of textile retail.",srcImg:"/images/industry/textiles.png"},{title:"Consumer Electronics",desc:"Enhance customer experience with seamless billing and efficient inventory control for electronic stores.",srcImg:"/images/industry/electronics.png"},{title:"Jewellery",desc:"Secure and precise billing solutions designed for high-value jewellery retail transactions.",srcImg:"/images/industry/jewellery.png"},{title:"Stationery",desc:"Organise inventory and simplify transactions for stationery stores with versatile retail solutions.",srcImg:"/images/industry/stationary.png"}]}},I2=({tag:e,heading:t,dolist:i})=>{var h;const[r,o]=S.useState(0),[c,u]=S.useState(((h=i[0])==null?void 0:h.srcImg)||null),m=S.useRef(null),f=g=>{var v;r===g?o(null):(o(g),u((v=i[g])==null?void 0:v.srcImg))};return S.useEffect(()=>{var g;if(r!==-1&&m.current){const v=m.current,x=(g=v.children[r])==null?void 0:g.offsetHeight;v.scrollTo({top:x*r,behavior:"smooth"})}},[r]),n.jsxs("div",{className:"container md:pt-20",children:[n.jsxs("p",{className:"flex items-center gap-3 pb-5 text-primary uppercase font-semibold md:pb-6",children:[n.jsx("span",{className:"block border-primary border-y w-11"}),e]}),n.jsx("h3",{className:"max-w-[860px] pb-10 md:pb-19 font-[250] leading-9 md:leading-